messages.text: If I left here 2nite, would U come w/ me?
If I left this town 2nite, would U take my hand and follow?
No, it means you made me smile.
Funny girl. So which is it?
Same as we do now.. Together, hand in hand.
And how would we eat? No one gives jobs to fifteen year olds.
Hmm.. We could beg, borrow and steal.
Sounds dangerous. Could we just borrow?
So we’ll come back 2 that 1. Gotcha. :P
What else would U like to know?
But we could send them postcards. ☺ Greetings from…
Well, there is the school thing.
NO 1 sees us when we’re there. Who would miss us if we’re gone?
I would miss U if U were gone!!!
Hence the question.. If I left here tonight…
Would I take your hand and follow?
That’s a very good question. It might take time 2 answer. Days even.
So.. You wouldn’t come with me? ☹
Ha! Didn’t say that. U R putting words into my fingers. :P
But you didn’t say yes, either.
I suppose it’s worth considering. After all, what future could this sleepy little town hold for the likes of us?
Like U just the way U R.
U R sweet.. But we digress..
Yes.. well.. Everyone says the best thing about this town is that it’s quiet.
Ah.. but what is quiet? It’s merely the absence of sound.
So if there is nothing but NOTHING here.. It must mean EVERYTHING is out THERE.
So U make my argument 4 me.
So, to recap.. there is NOTHING here except…?
So everything you want is already here?
So now ur arguing to stay?
Ah, but.. methinks you’ve forgotten my original question.
Methinks?? Really? Now ur what.. Romeo?
Why R U on my lawn in the middle of the night?
Im waiting 4 U to take my hand?
So come out on ur balcony.
It’s a flower box.. U nutter.
NO! The rents R still up.
So my dad will strangle U if he finds U.
He does. So go away B4 he doesn’t.
I’ll go when U stop smiling. ☺
How can I not smile when U R around?
How can I go when I see U smiling?
Good. Have something to show U then. Hang on.
There. What do U think of the new hat? Like it?
Maybe a little. But I still luv U.
Sorry. I luv U b/c U bring a little beauty into the world.
Good.. let’s end on that note. Will U be in school tomorrow?
Fingers crossed this one kicks it.
Now will U go B4 someone sees U?
I WOULD take ur hand and follow. ☺☺
Well we can’t have that, so…
